  "instructions": [
    "Heat 2 tablespoons of oil in a large Dutch oven over medium heat.",
    "Add the onion, carrots, and celery and cook until the vegetables are tender, about 10 minutes.",
    "Add the flour and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Whisk in the oat milk and bring to a boil.",
    "Add the brown sugar, salt, and black pepper, and stir to combine.",
    "Reduce the heat to low and simmer, covered, for 20 minutes.",
    "Stir in the bay leaves and cook for an additional 5 minutes.",
    "Serve hot, garnished with fresh herbs, if desired."
